BITWRITER

Upcoming
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Support for non-UTF-8 input files and strings added.


1.0.2  2015-07-26  Maintenance release
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Option -S removed (too technical, not really needed).
* Processing made to rely on the validator (saves code).
* Defaults in the XSDs made more precise.
* 0X and 0B accepted for hex and binary values.
* Minor fixes and improvements.


1.0.1  2015-07-22  Maintenance release
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* JDOM2 API requiring external JAR replaced with DOM.
* Minor fixes and improvements.


1.0.0  2015-07-20  Initial release
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Initial release, fully functional, no serious issues.
